<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.6.1">
<l>vāṇilā muṟuval ciṟunutal peruntōṇ</l>
<l>mātarār vaṉamulaip payaṉē</l>
<l>pēṇiṉē ṉataṉaip piḻaiyeṉak karutip</l>
<l>pētaiyēṉ piṟavinō yaṟuppā</l>
<l>ṉēṇilē ṉiruntē ṉeṇṇiṉē ṉeṇṇi</l>
<l>yiḷaiyavark kalaviyin tiṟattai</l>
<l>nāṇiṉēṉ vantuṉ tiruvaṭi yaṭaintēṉ</l>
<l>naimicā raṇiyat tuḷentāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I desired the pleasures of the lovely breasts of ample armed ladies</l>
<l rend="indent">with delicate foreheads and bright moonlight smiles;</l>
<l>Considering that as a fault, fool that I am,</l>
<l rend="indent">I was one without the resolve to end this disease of birth.</l>
<l>I reflected [on this]; having reflected, I was ashamed</l>
<l rend="indent">because of the embraces of tender maidens.</l>
<l>Coming [here], I took refuge at your divine feet, my father in Naimiśāraṇyam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
